Dependency:
    websocketpp - https://github.com/zaphoyd/websocketpp
    
    Requires:
        boost library 1.xx
        
        - successfully compiled and linked with 1.51
        - default boost library 1.46 of ubuntu 11.10 is insufficient

Linking:
    LDLIBS=-lwebsocketpp -lboost_system -lboost_date_time -lboost_regex -lboost_random -lboost_thread
    
    
